oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Zac Brown Band at the Bridgestone Arena

oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (light blue, brown, and gold on tan) announcing the Zac Brown Band at the Bridgestone Arena on December 29. Poster features a woodcut of a guitar and the heraldic bald eagle from the United State's Great Seal.
